item.content:encoded:
iOS Icon Gallery was born out of my desire to find a gallery showcasing icon designs within the iOS ecosystem (iPhone, iPad, iPod Touch, etc). This site was built by Jim Nielsen using a custom styled version of the Gallery Theme built on Thematic.

Feedback or Icon Suggestions
